  <summary>7/16/1997--Introduced.
Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to exempt from certain foreign student restrictions a public elementary or secondary school student who submits to the Attorney General evidence of the school's desire to enroll or reenroll such student. Prohibits use of Federal funds to pay for such enrollment.</summary>
